Available keypads: 0-9,*,#
Memory: a,b,c (number of vials in A, B and C: initially zero)
*: Yes
#: No

"Start the program?"
- Yes/No

	If Yes:
	"Do you want to refill the vials?"
	- Yes/No

		If Yes:
		"Number of vials in A: "
		- Digits
		"Number of vials in B: "
		- Digits
		"Number of vials in C: "
		- Digits

		If No:
		"Requirement: "
		- Digits
		"A: a, B: b, C: c"

	If No:
	"A: a, B: b, C: c"